  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1e946f4c-ab2c-4a82-7c29-d237c6182900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42643923240938164\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"2345\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505106774\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1e946f4c-ab2c-4a82-7c29-d237c6182900/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：LRS</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">80年代，当强化学习被冷落，这对师徒没有放弃；如今，重看来时路，他们给出的建议仍然是，「坚持」住自己的科研思想。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">3月5日，计算机学会（ACM）宣布Andrew Barto和Richard Sutton获得图灵奖，以表彰其在强化学习领域做出的奠基性贡献。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">自从9年前AlphaGo围棋大胜，引爆全民RL狂欢，再到如今Deepseek-R1等推理模型的火热，足以证明强化学习在人工智能领域的长久影响力。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6ea42a5f-2e62-4f08-d8cf-b83717cb7600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"864\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"505106267\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6ea42a5f-2e62-4f08-d8cf-b83717cb7600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近，Communications of the ACM发布了一段对师徒二人的采访，从强化学习的研究经历，聊到对人工智能的未来预测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Barto侧重于多智能体协作学习，Sutton则认为AGI还需要至少几十年，但最终一定能实现，二人对AI的未来以及强化学习的应用前景都充满希望！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">关于两人共同获得的100万美元图灵奖奖金，目前尚未确定具体用途。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Sutton表示可能将其份额捐赠给共同创立的Openmind研究所，给青年科学家提供「奢侈」的科研自由，让他们像自己当年那样专注探索基础性问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Barto则计划用奖金在马萨诸塞大学（UMass）设立研究生奖学金。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">强化学习萌芽</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1975年的斯坦福校园里，当时还是心理学专业的本科生Richard Sutton，翻遍了图书馆里所有关于机器智能的文献，认知受到了巨大冲击。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他对主流的「模式识别」和「示例学习」观点感到失望，认为动物并不是这么学习的，而是通过某种奖励反馈机制（They do things to get rewards.）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当时，唯一将奖励与学习联系起来的研究人员是美国空军实验室的A. Harry Klopf，认为脑细胞会主动寻求奖励。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Sutton立即决定给Klopf写信，并在1978年心理学毕业后，在马萨诸塞大学阿默斯特分校从事研究，主要工作就是测试Klopf的观点。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7365afd5-c57c-46ac-ea37-95d6fcb9f900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1971544715447155\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"984\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"984\" data-height=\"1178\" data-backw=\"377\" data-backh=\"451\" data-imgfileid=\"505106268\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7365afd5-c57c-46ac-ea37-95d6fcb9f900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">团队当时有一位博士后Andrew Barto，在接受空军和国家科学基金会长达五年的资助后，除了一份报告，并没有交付出任何成果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Barto于1970年获得密歇根大学数学学士学位，1975年获得计算机科学博士学位，最终成为UMass自适应网络实验室（现为自主学习实验室）的联合主任，2012年退休。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6051dd0-0d31-4bbd-d7d1-190b2f5e1f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"864\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"505106269\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6051dd0-0d31-4bbd-d7d1-190b2f5e1f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Sutton加入实验室后，成为了Barto的第一位博士生，二人最终发展出了现代强化学习技术，奖励也是其中的核心，通过设计奖励信号来训练神经网络，让神经元顺着预期方向发展。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/038b8bde-18a9-4ba9-900b-c044fb7a4c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2123687281213535\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"857\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"857\" data-height=\"1039\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"701\" data-imgfileid=\"505106270\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/038b8bde-18a9-4ba9-900b-c044fb7a4c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1984年，Sutton在马萨诸塞大学安姆斯特分校（University of Massachusetts at Amherst）获得了博士学位，直到1994年，Sutton都是GTE Laboratories的计算机和智能系统实验室的技术组的主要成员，随后又以资深研究科学家的身份回到了马萨诸塞大学安姆斯特分校。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">任职期间，Barto和Sutton共同出版了《强化学习导论》，获得了超8万次引用，2018年又发行了第二版，至今仍是全球AI学子的圣经。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/16985414-7b18-48c1-576a-2b74eb92ec00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2907407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1394\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"746\" data-imgfileid=\"505106272\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/16985414-7b18-48c1-576a-2b74eb92ec00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，Sutton加入AT&amp;T Shannon Laboratory担任人工智能部门的主要技术组成员，研究方向围绕着决策者与其环境交互时所面临的学习问题，持续改进自己对世界的表征和模型的系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2003年之后，Sutton成了阿尔伯塔大学计算机科学系的教授和 iCORE Chair，领导着强化学习与人工智能实验室（RLAI）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，说起强化学习的历史，Barto也提到，他们的思路并不新鲜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">早在1954年，人工智能先驱马文明斯基（Marvin Minsky）的博士学位论文主题就是模拟神经的强化学习系统，也是IBM计算机科学家Arthur Samuel用来训练计算机下棋的方法。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ba8a7e46-e3c8-4280-6c84-1bf0890c0400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49269311064718163\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"479\" style=\"width: 79%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"479\" data-height=\"236\" data-backw=\"479\" data-backh=\"236\" data-imgfileid=\"505106273\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ba8a7e46-e3c8-4280-6c84-1bf0890c0400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，到了20世纪70年代，这个想法已经过时，大多数AI研究员都在设计专家系统，Barto也庆幸自己能够保持「不合时宜」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Barto和Sutton提出的一个关键技术是「时间差分学习」（temporal difference learning）。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/020f4eb5-4b73-4b40-2b5f-afd94ed77700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8936170212765957\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1128\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1128\" data-height=\"1008\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"517\" data-imgfileid=\"505106274\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/020f4eb5-4b73-4b40-2b5f-afd94ed77700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如，想教一台计算机学习下棋，奖励信号如果是赢得游戏，那中间哪些动作步骤是正确的，仍然无法确定；即时奖励可以在计算机预测一步后，反馈出离最终奖励仍然有多少距离，比如胜率是否增加。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">预测随时间的变化（时间差）提供强化信号，那么在下次计算机下棋时，就可以采取那些能增加胜率的动作。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">破圈</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2016年，一场围棋人机大战，让强化学习广为人知，连学术圈之外的人都能聊两句「阿尔法狗」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Google DeepMind开发的AlphaGo，最终以四胜一败击败李世乭，赛后韩国棋院授予AlphaGo为荣誉九段。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e99770b6-9b91-4917-e308-8361eb5d8f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6186868686868687\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"792\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"792\" data-height=\"490\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"358\" data-imgfileid=\"505106275\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e99770b6-9b91-4917-e308-8361eb5d8f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2017年，AlphaGo Master以3：0的战绩，击败了世界排名第一的围棋棋手柯洁，从此人类棋手再无一人是机器的对手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以说，强化学习让「围棋」死了一半。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">之前的机器学习方法主要是有监督学习和无监督学习，在有监督设置下，人工标注样本给机器进行学习，样本量有限，无法适应「围棋」这种特征空间很大的情况；而无监督学习则是自动提取出有效特征，以在数据中找到结构。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0cfbb681-3a97-4959-686f-7c231b4fdf00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4666666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1235\" data-height=\"576\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"262\" data-imgfileid=\"505106276\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0cfbb681-3a97-4959-686f-7c231b4fdf00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这两种方法在计算中都已被证明是有用的，但都不是生物大脑的学习方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">强化学习的思路是，当神经网络实现了一个指定目标（比如赢得棋局）时，就会获得一定数值的奖励；如果失败了，会得到一个负值奖励。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">机器可以通过不断试错来学习，尝试不同的移动，最终学到了在不同场景下应该使用哪种移动方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此后，强化学习一路高歌猛进，不仅攻克了各种电子竞技游戏，还引发了大型语言模型的推理革命，比如OpenAI o系列、DeepSeek-R1等推理模型，已成为新的研究主流。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">人工智能的未来</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Barto预测人工智能领域将向多智能体强化学习（multi-agent RL）方向演进，由神经网络社群及其个体奖励系统将形成互动，这种机制可能进一步催生出协作网络，多个模型为实现共同目标而互相奖励，也可能引发持有不同目标的智能体之间的利益冲突。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此类交互将对经济学与博弈论等复杂领域产生深远影响。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Sutton则认为人工智能发展仍处于初级阶段，包括向通用人工智能（AGI）的探索，即机器能理解人类认知范围内的所有事物，Sutton坚信强化学习将在这一进程中发挥关键作用。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3de725f-d5f2-4337-e277-a72a679ef900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.334\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"667\" data-backw=\"500\" data-backh=\"667\" data-imgfileid=\"505106277\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3de725f-d5f2-4337-e277-a72a679ef900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谈到给年轻计算机研究人员的建议，Barton倡导效仿二人的科研路，勇敢追随自己的研究兴趣，不必在意领域内其他人的看法。虽然这很困难，但你必须找到内在驱动力，并尽你最大的能力坚持下去。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Sutton则给出更具体的建议，「坚持写作」，通过文字记录来锤炼思想。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一说起计算机科学的未来，Sutton就充满信心：未来几十年内，人类将彻底破解人工智能的奥秘！这有可能是史上最伟大的智力飞跃，能为其贡献绵薄之力是我们的荣幸。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://cacm.acm.org/news/a-rewarding-line-of-work/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5c01fefd-3c28-4443-6252-85fee59fbb00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5796296296296296\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"326\" data-imgfileid=\"505099958\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5c01fefd-3c28-4443-6252-85fee59fbb00/public\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "介绍了强化学习领域先驱 Andrew Barto 和 Richard Sutton 荣获图灵奖，回顾了他们的研究历程，以及他们对科研自由的重视和对人工智能未来发展的展望。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "介绍了强化学习领域先驱 Andrew Barto 和 Richard Sutton 荣获图灵奖，回顾了他们的研究历程，以及他们对科研自由的重视和对人工智能未来发展的展望。",
  "summary": "文章主要介绍了 Andrew Barto 和 Richard Sutton 因在强化学习领域的奠基性贡献而荣获图灵奖。文章回顾了两人在强化学习领域的研究历程，包括早期的探索、时间差分学习的提出，以及强化学习在 AlphaGo 等 breakthrough 应用中的突破。同时，文章也阐述了他们对人工智能未来发展的展望，Barto 认为多智能体强化学习是未来方向，而 Sutton 坚信强化学习将在通用人工智能的实现中发挥关键作用。文章还特别突出了两位学者对科研自由的重视，以及他们计划如何利用奖金来支持青年科学家的科研自由。",
